school_name: Vaughn College of Aeronautics and Technology
comments: Professor Murphy isn\'t teaching at Vaughn anymore, but I did take his ENG I course during my first semester in Jan. 2009. It was a memorable class, and Prof. Murphy always challenged his students with fun exercises, papers, and discussions. I hope he is happier wherever he is now, and that his future students might benefit from this review.

comments: Great professor really helpful. Seems really tough at first, but very fair!
